{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_06_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 思い出のスノードーム",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の仕事帰り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡWay back from work someday",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "予定よりも早く撮影が終わったな\n次の仕事までまだ時間があるが、どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shooting ended earlier than planned.\nWhat will you do until the next job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.632426389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私は一度事務所に戻ります。ライブの新曲について\nみんなで話し合っているので参加してきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll return to the office. There's a meeting about the new song\nfor the live performance‚ so I'll join them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの新曲会議か……\n曲作りの進捗はどんな感じなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A meeting for Moon Tempest's new song‚ huh…\nHow's the songwriting progress?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5577940609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.3922678788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "順調です。苦労も多いですが\nみんなで意見を出し合って楽しく曲作りをしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's going well. There are challenges‚\nbut we're all pitching in and enjoying this process.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.4919961453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "それに琴乃ちゃんの誕生日サプライズも計画して……\nあ、このことは秘密にして下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ we're planning a surprise birthday event for Kotono…\nOh‚ please keep this a secret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ。琴乃も喜んでくれるといいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got it. Hope Kotono will be happy about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4092978955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5793659688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、当日が楽しみです\n……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm looking forward to the day.\n…Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　急に立ち止まってどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Why did you suddenly stop?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。そこのショーウインドウに\n気になる物があったので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. I saw something that\ncaught my eye in that show window…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この店は雑貨屋か？　何が気になるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this a variety store? What caught your interest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "あのスノードームです。子供の頃、クリスマスに\nこれとよく似たプレゼントをもらったことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That snow globe. When I was a child‚\nI received a Christmas present very similar to that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか見ていると昔を思い出してしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just looking at it brings back memories…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "うちは両親が共働きなので\nクリスマスは千紗と二人で過ごすことが多かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My parents both worked‚\nso Christmas was often spent just with my sister Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗には寂しい思いをしてほしくなくて\n私はいろんなことをやりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't want Chisa to feel lonely‚\nso I tried many different things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にツリーを飾り付けしたり、二人でケーキ作りに\n挑戦したり、クリスマスの映画を観たり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We decorated the tree together‚ made a cake‚\n‚watched Christmas movies…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0215224207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "私がアイドルの真似をして部屋でライブをすると\n千紗は特に喜んでくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And when I pretended to be an idol\nand held a concert in the room‚ Chisa was especially happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が笑顔になるのを見て\n私もクリスマスを楽しく過ごせたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing Chisa's smile\nmade me enjoy Christmas too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "光景が目に浮かぶよ\n沙季と千紗は本当に仲のいい姉妹だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can picture it.\nYou and Chisa really are close sisters.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "私はお姉ちゃんですから\n妹の面倒を見るのは当然のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am her older sister‚ after all.\nLooking after my little sister is natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、大変なこともありましたけど\n嬉しいことも沢山あったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ there were tough times‚\nbut there were also many happy moments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "たとえば、クリスマスの朝は必ず\n枕元にプレゼントが置いてあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ every Christmas morning‚\nthere was always a present by our pillows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "朝起きると千紗と二人で「サンタさんが来た」って\nいつも喜んでいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we woke up‚ Chisa and I\nalways used to be delighted‚ saying \"Santa came\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2764177094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さっき言ってたスノードームも\nサンタからのクリスマスプレゼントだったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The snow globe you mentioned earlier\nwas also a Christmas present from Santa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "はい。そのスノードームは凄く綺麗で\n私は一目見て気に入りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. That snow globe was so beautiful\nthat I loved it at first sight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "それで四六時中スノードームを眺めていたら\n千紗も興味を持っちゃって……",
      "translations": {
